trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccessibleHandler" /> and all of its exposed members are part of a managed wrapper for the Component Object Model (COM) accessibility interface.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:Accessibility.IAccessibleHandler" /> e todos os seus membros expostos fazem parte de um wrapper gerenciado da interface de acessibilidade COM (Component Object Model).

trans-unit.source: For more information about <xref:Accessibility._RemotableHandle>, see the Microsoft Active Accessibility documentation in the MSDN library at http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações sobre <xref:Accessibility._RemotableHandle>, consulte a documentação do Microsoft Active Accessibility na biblioteca MSDN em http://msdn.microsoft.com/library.
